fwctl for Debian
----------------

changed the config dir to /etc/fwctl and /etc/fwctl/services/.
changed accounting file to /var/log/fwctl_acct.
changed init script to meet Debian's needs.
changed cron.d script to chek for /usr/sbin/fwctl. run dump-acct every 10 minutes
added logrotate entry to save accounting files weekly
added "flush" argument to fwctl to clear and remove all chains and rules and set policy to allow

